  "unmapped_findings": [
    "The review indicates that the fatigue behaviour and formability of Fe-Mn-Al-C steels cannot be properly understood at this stage due to limited experimental results.",
    "Information on weldability and coatability of these materials is still very much lacking.",
    "The Young's modulus of these steels is significantly lower than conventional high strength steels, which is a main issue for automotive applications.",
    "Industrial scale production remains a challenge due to high Al content causing processing problems like surface defects and cracking.",
    "The exact cause of the large difference in total elongation between studies on the same alloy composition is still unclear."
  ]
